Text: How about seeding for a while?

This file is a fake.

It is just a 17 second Universal intro with screen captions saying "Codec Error: Use Windows Media Player" and "Aborting Video, Redirecting to Microsoft Codec Download Page". Which is total crap.

I would advise you don't waste your 1gig download just to find this out: just take my word for it.

The original seeder is no longer around so you'll never even reach 100%.
